WEBVTT

00:03.732 --> 00:05.734
All around the world, 


00:05.733 --> 00:08.570
people come together 
every week at places 


00:08.570 --> 00:11.000
of worship called Kingdom Halls.


00:14.285 --> 00:16.495
Have you ever wondered what happens 


00:16.495 --> 00:19.000
inside a Kingdom Hall 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses?


00:20.707 --> 00:23.294
It’s a place where Bible study programs 


00:23.293 --> 00:26.000
and lectures are held each week.


00:27.757 --> 00:30.634
The first time I attended a meeting, 


00:30.633 --> 00:32.135
I felt very happy. 


00:32.135 --> 00:33.887
The atmosphere was so good; 


00:33.887 --> 00:36.000
I’ve never seen 
anything like it anywhere else.


00:38.350 --> 00:41.562
The people are loving, orderly, 


00:41.562 --> 00:44.000
and show an interest in people.


00:46.608 --> 00:48.985
Every meeting is open to the public. 


00:48.985 --> 00:53.157
Seats are free and no 
collections are ever taken.


00:53.157 --> 00:58.000
Families are invited 
to attend and learn together.


00:59.455 --> 01:04.000
All meetings begin and end 
with song and prayer.


01:05.085 --> 01:08.630
One meeting, 
usually held on the weekend, 


01:08.630 --> 01:10.882
includes a 30-minute 
Bible discourse 


01:10.882 --> 01:13.885
especially designed 
for the general public.


01:13.885 --> 01:17.138
After that, there’s 
a question-and-answer discussion 


01:17.138 --> 01:21.101
based on an article in the study edition 
of the Watchtower magazine. 


01:21.102 --> 01:23.770
Participation is always voluntary.


01:23.770 --> 01:26.607
At one of the meetings during the week, 


01:26.607 --> 01:28.775
we not only study the Bible 


01:28.775 --> 01:31.000
but also receive training 
in public speaking.


01:34.072 --> 01:38.744
Everyone is invited 
to the Christian meetings, 


01:38.743 --> 01:42.000
including those who are not 
Jehovah’s Witnesses.


01:44.333 --> 01:46.918
You can go into any Kingdom Hall 


01:46.918 --> 01:50.000
and receive the same program 
of Bible instruction.


01:52.633 --> 01:55.843
Bible education, upbuilding association, 


01:55.843 --> 01:59.096
and the opportunity 
to praise God await you 


01:59.097 --> 02:03.000
at Christian meetings 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.


02:05.478 --> 02:07.898
To find a Kingdom Hall near you, 


02:07.898 --> 02:10.756
please visit the About Us section 


02:10.757 --> 02:25.312
and fill in 
the congregation meeting search.

